high_descs: Pick up the glass vase from the TV stand.
Turn around and face the coffee table.
Place the vase onto the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Put the glass vase on the coffee table.

high_descs: Walk to stand in front of the TV.
Pick up the gray vase from the TV stand.
Turn around and walk to the coffee table.
Place the vase on the coffee table at the right hand corner of the right laptop on the table.
anns.task_desc: Pick up a vase, place it on the coffee table

high_descs: Walk forward until you're past the coffee table, turn left and walk forward till you're past it again, then turn right to face the tv stand
Pick up the bowl from the tv stand
Turn right, walk forward a step, then turn right again to face the coffee table
Place the bowl beside the right laptop on the coffee table
anns.task_desc: Move the bowl from the TV stand to the coffee table.
